How to install
--------------

1. Clone or download a tarball/zip of this repo
2. Open chrome and switch to the "extension manager"
3. Enable "developer mode"
4. Choose "load unpacked extension" and select the directory where you put the files
5. Click on Options/or the gray Team City icon in the toolbar
6. Enter you base TeamCity url including basic auth.
   E.g: http://username:password@tcserver.local:8080

   ** Note: don't write any trailing slash (/) in the url **
